OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fmainly dry and settled few days with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunshine although the east
OL,8,Fcoast may see haar on Saturday.
OL,9,FBecoming very warm or hot, but the
OL,10,Feast coast cooler.
